trans-unit.source: Specifies whether a printer uses one-sided printing or some type of two-sided (duplex) printing.
trans-unit.target: Angir om en skriver bruker Ensidig utskrift eller en type begge sider () dupleksutskrift.

trans-unit.source: Use the values of this type primarily for these purposes: - As members of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.DuplexingCapability%2A> collection, which is a property of <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>, these values indicate the kinds of one-sided and two-sided printing that the printer supports.
trans-unit.target: Bruk verdiene i denne typen først og fremst for dette formålet: – som medlemmer av den <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.DuplexingCapability%2A>samling, som er en egenskap av <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>, disse verdiene indikerer typer Ensidig og begge sider utskrift som skriveren støtter.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.DuplexingCapability%2A>

trans-unit.source: - As the value of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Duplexing%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>, they direct the printer to use one-sided printing or some kind of two-sided printing.
trans-unit.target: -Som verdien for den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Duplexing%2A>for en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>, de direkte skriveren bruke Ensidig utskrift eller noen form for begge sider utskrift.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Duplexing%2A>

trans-unit.source: The **Unknown** value is never used in properties of <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den **ukjent** verdien aldri er brukt i Egenskaper for <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>objekter.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>

trans-unit.source: You should never set a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> property to **Unknown**.

If some other <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> producing application has created a *PrintTicket document* that sets the duplexing feature to an unrecognized duplexing option (that is, an option that is not defined in the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)), then a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> object in your application that is constructed with that document will have **Unknown** as the value of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Duplexing%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis noen andre <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>produserer applikasjonen er opprettet en *PrintTicket dokumentet* som angir dupleksfunksjon til et ukjent dupleksing alternativ (som er et alternativ som ikke er definert i den [Skriv ut skjemaet](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)), og deretter en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>objektet i programmet som er laget med dette dokumentet har **ukjent** som verdien for den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Duplexing%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Duplexing%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: Although the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> classes cannot be inherited, you can extend the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397) to recognize print device features that are not accounted for in the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> or <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> classes.
trans-unit.target: Selv om den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>og <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>klasser kan arves, kan du utvide den [skrive ut skjemaet](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397) ikke gjenkjenne skriver funksjoner som ikke blir inkludert i den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>eller <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>klasser.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: For more information see [NOTINBUILD: How to: Extend the Print Schema and Create New Print System Classes](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a3600218-1ea5-478a-9853-6560464f2885).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon se [NOTINBUILD: slik: utvide Skriv ut skjemaet og opprette nye utskrift systemklasser](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a3600218-1ea5-478a-9853-6560464f2885).

trans-unit.source: Output prints on only one side of each sheet.
trans-unit.target: Output skriver ut på bare den ene siden av hvert ark.

trans-unit.source: Output prints on both sides of each sheet, which flips along the edge parallel to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintDocumentImageableArea.MediaSizeHeight*>.
trans-unit.target: Output skriver på begge sider av hvert ark blar langs kanten parallelt <xref:System.Printing.PrintDocumentImageableArea.MediaSizeHeight*>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintDocumentImageableArea.MediaSizeHeight*>

trans-unit.source: Output prints on both sides of each sheet, which flips along the edge parallel to <xref:System.Printing.PrintDocumentImageableArea.MediaSizeWidth*>.
trans-unit.target: Output skriver på begge sider av hvert ark blar langs kanten parallelt <xref:System.Printing.PrintDocumentImageableArea.MediaSizeWidth*>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintDocumentImageableArea.MediaSizeWidth*>

trans-unit.source: The feature (whose options are represented by this enumeration) is set to an option not defined in the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397).
trans-unit.target: Funksjonen (alternativer som er representert av denne opplisting) er satt til et alternativ som ikke er definert i den [Skriv ut skjemaet](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397).
